sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as Quan tri vien
    participant UI as Document UI
    participant API as RAG Admin API
    participant Store as Object Storage
    participant Parser as Parser/OCR
    participant Chunker as Chunker
    participant Emb as Embedding Service
    participant VDB as Vector DB
    participant Meta as Metadata DB

    Admin->>UI: Upload tai lieu
    UI->>API: POST /rag/documents
    API->>Store: Luu file goc
    API->>Parser: Trich xuat text, table, metadata
    Parser-->>API: Parsed content
    API->>Chunker: Chia chunk theo heading/token
    Chunker-->>API: Chunks
    loop Moi chunk
        API->>Emb: Tao embedding
        Emb-->>API: Vector
        API->>VDB: Upsert vector + chunk text + metadata
    end
    API->>Meta: Luu document status=INGESTED
    API-->>UI: Ingest thanh cong
